Cam::  

She picked up the baby and held her over her shouder in a slightly 
off attempt to help the baby rid air trapped in the energy absorbancy 
systems. She patted the little bot on the back while holding her. 

"Ok, now that your fed, what am I going to do with you? So far, we're 
ok here. but from what I can make out, there are some really mean 
bots outside somewhere.  So, I don't know if we should stay put 
untill the computer tells us to make a run for it? Or do we go hide 
somewhere now?"  She decided to walk around the base. She carried the 
baby in her small child arms and tried to be a big bot for her and 
the baby. She just walked around the halls, talking in a soft voice 
and trying to keep the baby calm despite the fact that her own fears 
were growing.
